Rating: 3
Very good, very simple. I ended up having to make it on the stovetop in a heavy cast iron Dutch oven (I don't have an oven in my new house!) but it still worked beautifully, and the sauce thickened nicely. I used half anf half simply because I was out of cream, but I'd recommend doing it that way any time. Was still very creamy and delicious. The time honored test of tastiness: even my three year-old loved it. A bit of crumbled bacon would be a nice addition as a topping.

